3. **Pour chaque ticket commence**: `heg-state start --ticket CAB-XXXX --role frontend --branch feat/...`
4. **Linear**: `linear.update_issue(id, state="In Progress")`
5. Travailler 1 ticket a la fois, micro-PRs (<300 LOC)

